## Default Browser Fonts

| Browser | sans-serif | serif | monospace |
|---------|------------|-------|-----------|
| Safari | Helvetica | Times | Courier |
| Chrome | Helvetica | Times | Courier |
| Firefox | Helvetica | Times New Roman | Courier |
| Opera | Helvetica | Times | Courier |


